# {{ project_name }}

RAG Agent template generated by `create-agent-app`.

## Template Overview

This project combines:
- ChromaDB local vector store
- sentence-transformers embeddings
- retrieval tool + LangGraph agent loop

Use it when answers must be grounded in local documents.

## Architecture

```text
sample_docs/*.txt
   |
   v
[ingest.py] -> chunk -> embed -> [ChromaDB]
                                |
User Question ------------------+
                                v
                       [Retriever Tool]
                                |
                                v
                         [Agent Node]
                                |
                                v
                               [END]
```

## Setup

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # Windows: .venv\\Scripts\\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
cp .env.example .env
# Configure provider key(s) in .env
python main.py
```

